* RoboSim - Robot simulator

** Build Instruction
   To Build the sources please use Apache Ant

   |-------------+------------------------------------------|
   | Ant target  | Action                                   |
   |-------------+------------------------------------------|
   | ant compile | to compile the sources                   |
   | ant deploy  | to deploy a .jar file into the dist/ dir |
   | ant run     | to start the programm                    |
   | ant clean   | to delete the compiled sources           |
   |-------------+------------------------------------------|

** Key Bindings

   |----------------+------------------------------------------|
   | Key            | Action                                   |
   |----------------+------------------------------------------|
   | CURSOR         | Move cursor                              |
   | HOME           | Move cursor to the beginning of the line |
   | END            | Move cursor to the end of the line       |
   | PAGE_UP        | Move cursor to the top of the column     |
   | PAGE_DOWN      | Move cursor to the bottom of the column  |
   | MOUSE_BUTTON_1 | Move cursor to the mouse position        |
   |----------------+------------------------------------------|
   | SHIFT          | Set mark                                 |
   | ESC            | Unset mark                               |
   |----------------+------------------------------------------|
   | DEL            | Remove robot from cursor field           |
   | SPACE          | Set empty field                          |
   | r              | Set/rotate robot                         |
   | f              | Set floor field                          |
   | w              | Set wall field                           |
   | o              | Set obstacle field                       |
   |----------------+------------------------------------------|

** Shortcuts

   |----------+--------------------------|
   | Shortcut | Action                   |
   |----------+--------------------------|
   | CTRL-n   | New map                  |
   | CTRL-o   | Open map                 |
   | CTRL-s   | Save map                 |
   | CTRL-w   | Save map as              |
   | CTRL-q   | Exit                     |
   | CTRL-a   | Add Columns/Lines to map |
   |----------+--------------------------|

** Valid characters in a 'rmf' (RoboSim-Map-File)
   
   |-----------+------------------------------|
   | Character | Field                        |
   |-----------+------------------------------|
   | SPACE     | Empty field                  |
   | w         | Wall field                   |
   | f         | Floor field                  |
   | o         | Obstacle field               |
   | >         | Robot field (Rotation: 0째)   |
   | ^         | Robot field (Rotation: 90째)  |
   | <         | Robot field (Rotation: 180째) |
   | v         | Robot field (Rotation: 270째) |
   |-----------+------------------------------|
  

